18/03/2007
ANKARA, Turkey -- Prime Minister Recep Tayyip Erdogan says his Justice and Development Party (AKP) will announce its candidate for the May presidential election in mid to late April.
Speaking on Friday (March 16th), he suggested that there might be more than one nominee, with the choice to be made during the course of the campaign.
(Zaman - 17/03/07;
NTV - 16/03/07)
